*Step 1: Defining simple constants

constants c1(2) type c value 'AA'.
constants c2 like c1 value 'BB'.
constants error_threshold type i value 5.
constants amalgamation_date like sy-datum value '20200710'.
constants pie TYPE p DECIMALS 2 VALUE '3.14'.


WRITE : c1, c2, error_threshold, amalgamation_date, pie.
